 is love.&apos; His nature, His law, is love. It ever has </div><div class="t mf49 x92 he y11bd ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">been; it ever will be. . . . Every manifestation of creative power is an </div><div class="t m40e x92 he y1091 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">expression of infinite love.&quot;—&quot;Patriarchs and Prophets,&quot; p. 33. </div><div class="t m104a x18 he y1557 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m41d x61 he y1443 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How is divine love manifested to the human race? John 3:16. </div><div class="t mdd0 x18 he ya9d ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NOTE.—&quot;Only as we contemplate the great plan of redemption can </div><div class="t m66f x92 he y14d1 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">we have a just appreciation of the character of God. The work of crea-</div><div class="t m30a x92 he y146a ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tion was a manifestation of His love; but the gift of God to save the </div><div class="t m65e x92 he y11cb ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">guilty and ruined race, alone reveals the infinite depths of divine ten- </div><div class="t m116e x43 he y20e5 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">[9</div><div class="t m19aa x2f h84 y20e5 ff2 fs1e fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">] </div><div class="t m2a0d x1b h84 y20e3 ff2 fs1e fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
